data.description: Beautiful One Story Home near Celina High School, Moore Middle School and NEW Martin Elementary School. Buffalo Ridge has No PID No MUD, and  low HOA fees.  This open floor-plan offers large windows framing the large private back yard.  Split bedrooms with the 4th bedroom in the perfect location for an office or study.  Enjoy the large separate tub and walk in closet in the owners suite.  Beautiful wood floors and stained cabinets give it an elegant and luxurious look.  Home is North facing in a quiet neighborhood with no through traffic. Watch the sun set around the fire pit in the large back yard. Patio is perfect for grilling and entertaining while watching the kids and pets play.  Get the Small town feel in a growing community.
